OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBlustery showers, heavy at
OL,6,Ftimes, in the northwest. Some showers
OL,7,Fare possible elsewhere in the west,
OL,8,Fotherwise many areas will be largely
OL,9,Fdry with sunny spells and lighter
OL,10,Fwinds. Rather cold in the northwest,
OL,11,Felsewhere temperatures more towards
OL,12,Faverage.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FShowers ease to leave clear
OL,15,Fskies and a chilly evening. Overnight,
OL,16,Frain pushes in from the west with some
OL,17,Fhill snow in Scotland. Temperatures
OL,18,Ffall below freezing, bringing patchy
OL,19,Ffrost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
