OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FSunny spells to start in the
OL,6,Feast on Sunday. Rain will continue to
OL,7,Fspread eastwards, soon clearing to
OL,8,Fsunny spells and showers, heavy at
OL,9,Ftimes. Coastal gales in the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
